Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!\NWe've already been eaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight ahead! Straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakoku Sovereignty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nami's Sick?\NBeyond the Snow Falling on the Sea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're flying out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look back!\NWe're going straight ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huge! It's so huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They cut... the very sea itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the strength of Elbaf warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, there were ruffians on the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,known as the Giant Warrior Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two pirate bosses,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Ogre Broggy and Blue Ogre Dorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were exceptionally strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were left mostly unchecked,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for ordinary people no longer\Nstood a chance against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they say that the one who\Nput an end to their attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was a single little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see what our bosses caught today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's stuck in my mind!\NMy excitement won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each one of 'em bagged an\Ninsanely huge Sea King, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're Elbaf giants,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nobody can take down those\Njumbo-sized beasts except for our bosses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--You got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those ones were definitely\Nthe biggest ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! The biggest ones\Nwe've ever caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So which one was bigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Which...\N--...one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Who won the hunting contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Broggy! Mine is slightly bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish! Mine's a whole\N3 centimeters bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say what?!\N--What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:05:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bosses! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, Broggy. There's one\Nthing I can't seem to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, actually, that goes for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Middle Mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter! Let's just finish this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We can think things\Nthrough after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Someday, I will go to Elbaf!\NTo the village of warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Gi-Gi-Giants! Gi-Giants! #
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Elbaf-baf! Elbaf-baf! #
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Everyone's huge!\N'Cause they're giants! #
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# They're huge!\NThey're huge! They're huge! #
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are full of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm suddenly exhausted after\Neverything that's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi. Could you watch\Nthis compass for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can finally return to Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, assuming we can make\Nit there safely, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I must return!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the only way to\Nsave the kingdom, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The king-- your father-- no longer\Nhas sway with the people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.92,0:06:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only hope of\Nstopping this uprising now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is for you to tell the\Npeople the truth directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, no matter what, you must not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must live on, even if it\Nmeans losing those near to you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or having to betray others!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be painful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Vivi!\NAre you prepared not to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will return to Alabasta, alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to push\Nyourself so hard, Vivi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's relaxing sweets.\NHow about some petit fours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For drinks, you have your\Nchoice of coffee or tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is in the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:08:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2,603!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2,604!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2,605!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2,606!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could've cut that wax...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I wouldn't have left anyone hanging...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm gonna get stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I need to be able to cut up\Nstuff like that from any stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:41.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Alabasta Kingdom Sandy Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 2! Bon Clay-sama!\NThe Swanda is ready to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay! You're so loud, sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, now! Why do I have to do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 3 is nothing but bulky garbage!\NYou guys go toss him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't stand a chance,\Neven if we ganged up on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please! It is the boss' orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un, deux, trois...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.45,0:09:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "four" called?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:14.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bon Clay"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero-chan is so high-maintenance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi... Sorry. I think I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...go lie down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep an eye on our course.\NYou should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, come here! This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it, Vivi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san has a terrible fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:10:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Nami-san does?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nami-san gonna die? Is she, Vivi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's most likely the climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the obstacles all sailors\Nwho enter the Grand Line run into
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is illness caused by abnormal weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are countless stories\Nof tough, notorious pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,suddenly dying from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carelessness makes even\Nthe slightest case deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone on this ship with\Nany medical knowledge at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But eating meat makes\Nsickness go away! Right, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make some basic food\Nmeant for sick people,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's entirely\Nin "nursing" territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee\Nit'd make her better...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I normally put\N100 times more care
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into Nami-san and Vivi-chan's\Nmeals than I do with yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I serve them fresh meat and\Nvegetables, for balanced nutrition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I give all the\Nrotting stuff to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still good, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, as long\Nas I'm this ship's cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:12:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll be no problems whatsoever\Nin terms of getting a balanced diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are different kinds\Nof meals for sick people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are her symptoms? What does\Nshe need? I can't make that call...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she can just eat it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sick because she doesn't\Nhave the energy for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,40°C?! Her fever's gone up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be doctors when\Nwe get to Alabasta, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer will it take, Vivi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but one week\Nis out of the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is being sick that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno. Never been sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world are you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's bad!\N40°C fevers don't happen every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be a life-threatening illness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami's gonna die?!\N--Don't die, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a doctor to help Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Just calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to make\Nher illness even worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! She's all better!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get real!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my desk drawer...\Nthere's a newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No change in course...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it about Alabasta, Vivi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,300,000 royal soldiers\Ndefected to the Resistance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was originally a cold war,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with 600,000 royal soldiers and\N400,000 Resistance soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that's suddenly changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The uprising in Alabasta is\Nfinally going to get serious now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That paper's from three days ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. We can't change our speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't want to worry\Nyou by showing you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things seem very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, that got through to\Nyou more than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you need to see a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine... That thermometer\Nmust be broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody gets a temperature of 40°C...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just\Nsunstroke or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need a doctor.\NI'll get better on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's head straight\Nfor Alabasta as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! She's better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot. She's just acting tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, so much blood will\Nbe shed throughout the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be an all-out war...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't stop that,\Nthe Alabasta Kingdom will be done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile will take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just return safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to return as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't make it in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a million citizens will\Nkill themselves pointlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a million people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an immense burden\Nyou're carrying, Vivi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh! What were you\Nwatching all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya talking about?\NThe ship's been going straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, straight at a right angle!\NLook at the compass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to.\NI was watching that big cloud there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clouds move and change shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez, my head's killing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just leave this to me and go to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here because\NI can't leave this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air's changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air? It's been nice\Nweather this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! Just get the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get out here, you guys!\NGot work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hard to feel motivated\Nwhen you're giving the orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the seat and\Ncatch the portside wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waves are quiet,\Nand the weather's nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An immense wind...\Nis coming directly this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hot! Yeah, you stay inside\Nthe ship! Let's go to a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!\NThis is my normal temperature!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now quit being stupid and pull the ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san. I know you're\Nsaying that for Vivi-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you push too hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami. I think you really should--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry and move the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems a little different than a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry back to Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's not my place to ask\Nthis as a passenger on your ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but my homeland is in a terrible state now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd like to hurry ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't waste even a single minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want this ship to head for\NAlabasta at its fastest speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! That's what we promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's find an island with\Na doctor on it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cure Nami-san as quickly as\Npossible and then go to Alabasta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's this ship's fastest speed, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We can't go any faster than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As their princess, you should be\Nworried about those million citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! So we need to hurry\Nand cure Nami-san's illness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said, Vivi-chan!\NI've fallen for you all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overexert yourself, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Vivi... I think...\NI am kind of... in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! That's the direction--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the direction our\Nship was just headed in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been a direct hit\Nhad we kept going straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! We just barely made it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Line cyclones are said\Nto be impossible to predict!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, she--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't predict weather\Nbased on standard theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost as if she's detecting\Nthe weather with her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such a navigator before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's hurry, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go find us a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Vivi-chan?!\NNami-san's fever won't go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san! Karoo!\NI asked you to stop freaking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See any doctors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you expect him to, you idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys. Do you think\Npeople can stand on the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can people stand on the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Zoro. What kind of question is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is awfully big
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so even if there is treasure somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the odds are astronomical
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So relying on dumb luck\Nwon't get you anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.89,0:22:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if someone stops me or\Nlaughs at me from the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ship will continue forward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm a fool, but I gotta go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crazier the dream,\Nthe cooler the ambition
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm a fool, but I'm gonna fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The farther the sea,\Nthe more heavenly it surely is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do everything you can, and you'll\Nget a little nearer to any horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for not being\Nable to lower your fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to cool your head off!\NLook around!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's being attacked right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.62,0:23:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's it? Nothing's worse\Nthan Nami-san being sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! He's eating our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.23,0:23:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Raid! Tin Tyrant\Nand Tin Plate Wapol"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
